<h1 class="font-weight-bold text-left py-3 px-md-5">Solicitudes de sangre</h1>
<p class="text-left px-md-5">A continuaci√≥n se muestran las solicitudes de sangre activas <a href="/blood-request/add">Crea una</a> si lo necesitas c:</p>

<div class="container col-11">
    <table class="table table-sm" data-search="true">
        <thead>
            <tr>
                <th scope="col">Grupo sanguineo</th>
                <th scope="col">Unidades (450cc)</th>
                <th scope="col">Fecha fin</th>
                <th scope="col">Estado</th>
                <th scope="col">Sexo donante</th>
                <th scope="col">Lugar</th>
                <th scope="col">Banco de sangre</th>
            </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
            {{#each blood_requests}}
            <tr>
                <td>
                    <a type="button" class="btn-circle">{{grupo_sanguineo}}</a>
                </td>
                <td>{{cantidad}}</td>
                <td>{{fecha_fin}}</td>
                <td>{{estado}}</td>
                <td>{{sexo_donante}}</td>
                <td>{{lugar}}</td>
                <td>{{banco_sangre}}</td>
                <td>
                    <a href="/blood-request/donation/{{id}}" type="button" class="btn btn-primary pl-4 pr-4">Donar</a>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <a href="/blood-request/edit/{{id}}" type="button" class="btn btn-secondary pl-4 pr-4">Editar</a>
                </td>
                <td>
                    <a href="/blood-request/delete/{{id}}" type="button" class="btn btn-danger pl-4 pr-4">Eliminar</a>
                </td>
            </tr>
            {{/each}}
        </tbody>
    </table>
</div>